      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Bileams us\nta KUNGA Engeti : Es esmu\ngrehkojis/ jo es ne esmu finnajis/\ntew us Zeltu man pretti stah-\nwim/ un uu/ ja tas tew ne pa-\ntihk/ tad eeschu es atpakkat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNga\nEngelis us Bileamu : Eij lihds\nar teem Wihreem/ tomehr scho\nMahrdtu ween/ ko es us tew run-\nnaschu/ to buhs tew runnaht.\nTa gahje Bileams ar teem Ba-\nlaka Leeleem-Kungeein.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad uu Balaks dsirdeja\nBileamu nahkam/ tad isgahje\nwinsh tain pretti/ uhs to Moa-\nbiteru Pilsfahtu/ kas pee Arno-\nxa Rohbeschas irr/ ta irr ta peh-\ndiga Rohbescha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Balaks fazzija us\nBileamu: woj ne esmu es leetu\nSuhtifchanu pee tew fuhtijis\ntew aizinaht/kapehz tu ne esi pee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Bileams uu\nBalaku : Reds/ es esmu pe-\ntew nahzis/ woj es jebku warri\nrunnaht/ bes to Wahrdtu tween\nko Deews manna Muttê liks/t\nrunnaschu es.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Bileams gahje a\nBalaku/ un tee nahze Kirtat\nRizotâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Balaks nokawe lee-\nlus uu fihkus Lohpus/ un fuhtij-\npehz Bileamu/ un pehz teem Lee-\nleem-Kungeem/ kas pee winnu-\nbija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rihta Deena nehmi\nBalaks to Bileamu/ un wedd\nto Baala Kalnds/ ka winsh n-\nturrenes eerandfitu tohs Laudi-\nlihds gallugallam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad fazzija Bileams uu\nBalaku : Uhstaifi ma-\nscheitan feptin Altarus\nun fataisi man sche feptin Wehr-\nschns/ un feptin Aunn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad darrija Balaks ta-\nittin ka Bileams fazzijis bij/ uu\nBalaks/ un Bileams uppureje-\nweenu Wehrfi/ un weenu Auni-\nus ikweenu Altari.\n"
